pageContext.claim: “Cuomo wants 'all states to be treated the same.' But all states aren't the same. Some are being hit hard by the Chinese Virus, some are being hit practically not at all. New York is a very big 'hotspot', West Virginia has, thus far, zero cases. Andrew, keep politics out of it...”
pageContext.analysis: The U.S. testing apparatus was still catching up in mid-March, meaning many, many cases were still not diagnosed. In other words, there’s plenty of reason to suspect that there were cases of covid-19 in West Virginia.
